attributes.action: Weekly briefing on the tangible benefits of Brexit
attributes.additional_details: The Government needs to show the people tangible benefits of BREXIT. The tangible benefits of the new situation should be a mechanism to reduce the divided situation the country finds itself in.
attributes.background: I would like the Government to prepare and share with the population tangible information about how Brexit is improving the lives of the people. This must be backed up with clear facts and figures which can be understood by a lay person.
